.container
  %section#when
    .page-header
      %h1
        %i.icon-time
        %span When and where
        %small The dealio, yo

    %p 
      %span The ceremony and the reception at Willowdale Estate. It all starts at
      %strong 5:00 PM
      %span , with the reception right afterwards.

    %address
      %span Willowdale Estate
      %br
      %span 24 Asbury St
      %br
      %span Topsfield, MA

    %p Things you need to know:

    %ul
      %li Dress as casually as you'd like. Isaac won't be wearing a tie, if that helps.
      %li Hats highly encouraged
      %li Open bar.
      %li We'll be busing people to and from the hotels (see below).
