  %section#travel
    .page-header
      %h1
        %i.icon-plane
        %span Travel and accommodations
        %small Hotels, airports, that kind of thing

    %h2 Hotels

    %p
      We have a block of rooms at the 
      %strong
        %a(href="http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/massachusetts/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-boston-north-shore-BOSNSDT/index.html") North Shore DoubleTree
      and 
      %strong will also be providing a shuttle from there to Willowdale. So if you stay there, you won't have to drive.

    %p If for some reason, that just isn't your bag, here are some alternatives:

    %ul
      %li
        %a(href="http://www.comfortinn.com/hotel-danvers-massachusetts-MA081?source=gglocaljn") Comfort Inn
        in Danvers
      %li
        %a(href="http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/BOSDV-Courtyard-Boston-Danvers") Courtyard
        in Danvers

    %p But you should really stay in the DoubleTree if you can. Here's a handy map with the hotels (<font color="red">red</font>) and the venue (<font color="blue">blue</font>):
    <iframe width="640" height="480" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=213756666646673663709.0004d70cff084fda97949&amp;msa=0&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.6044,-70.941124&amp;spn=0.121296,0.219727&amp;z=12&amp;output=embed"></iframe><br /><small>View <a href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=213756666646673663709.0004d70cff084fda97949&amp;msa=0&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.6044,-70.941124&amp;spn=0.121296,0.219727&amp;z=12&amp;source=embed" style="color:#0000FF;text-align:left">Wedding Locations</a> in a larger map</small>

    %section
      %h2 Getting there

      %p You can either:

      %ul
        %li Drive to your hotel, park, and jump on one of the buses we chartered to take you to and from the hotel. That's what we recommend.
        %li Just drive to the venue. There's plenty of parking.

      %p The easiest thing to do is to fly into Logan Airport and drive. Directions to the venue from different places:

      %ul
        %li
          %strong from Boston Logan Airport: 
          Follow signs to Route 1A N towards Revere (it will take you briefly onto I90 E). Take 1A 2.5 miles and take a slight left onto MA-60 W. Take that to Route 1 N. Travel on Route 1 N for 16 miles and take a right onto Ipswitch Road. After 1 mile, take a right onto Asbury St. Willowdale is on the left about a quarter mile down.
        %li
          %strong from Boston proper: 
          Get on Route 1 N and take it for about 24 miles, into Topsfield. Take a right onto Ipswitch Road. After 1 mile, take a right onto Asbury St. Willowdale is on the left about a quarter mile down.
        %li
          %strong from New York City: 
          Drive north.

